{"tid":2046352,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"與其係行動上反Antifa，點解唔係從根本思想上反antifa — anticom？","createTime":"2020-06-01T10:52:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-01T14:25:19.000Z","uid":201464,"like":12,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c6276752c73444a1134084c25a5a9b231b7c5735","tid":2046352,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T10:52:18.000Z","msg":"Antifa 係咪中共背後有份搞未能證實<br />\n種族矛盾係美國一直存在係鐵一般嘅事實<br />\nGay巴所講嘅變藍絲就係好容易為咗反Antifa唔覺意牽涉入種族矛盾<br />\n為咗反Antifa不知不覺間反埋黑人 同藍絲小粉紅有乜分別？<br />\n如果真係要反Antifa，就實行思想上反Antifa，亦即係Anticom &mdash; 反對共產主義，抗衡Antifa。<br />\n呢一點亦可以話係成場運動嘅重心之一，亦可以清楚咁係意識上同Antifa割蓆。<br />\n#Anticom"},{"pid":"9a408333dcc4cd10b39727e76148cd897e30e2bb","tid":2046352,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T10:54:05.000Z","msg":"#Anticom"},{"pid":"8247dc571884fb5d61d44cbd9449665a0bc8dd1c","tid":2046352,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T10:56:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>#Anticom</blockquote>"},{"pid":"9c4ac370bf64bd023685ed9e7a453341cbd1111f","tid":2046352,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T11:00:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>#Anticom</blockquote>"},{"pid":"17597bed9820b428a10b3ef997bbc6536ee7cf10","tid":2046352,"uid":299171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T11:01:55.000Z","msg":"Antantifa"},{"pid":"7429855fb3df8f199dcd85b0055ddce17d33d228","tid":2046352,"uid":53604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T11:02:23.000Z","msg":"前BLM搞手爆料：索羅斯同 Clintons 係背後推動 Antifa 騎劫 BLM 運動<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2046310\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2046310</a>"},{"pid":"dfea6da8daf110cc545a309d590ab650bcd40fcd","tid":2046352,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7429855fb3df8f199dcd85b0055ddce17d33d228","tid":2046352,"uid":53604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime